freetext.SYMPTOMS_DESCRIPTION: Swollen lymph node L Axilla and L breast of the vaccine arm side on Wednesday. No redness, but it was sore.  Warm compresses and ibuprofen used and symptoms resolved by Saturday. Had I not been a healthcare provider, I would have seen one.
